summary: AN ORDINANCE Relating to land use and zoning, amending Plat 73W, page 173, and Plat 73E, page 174, of the Official Land Use Map, to rezone properties near the proposed Othello light rail station; generally located along Martin Luther King Jr. Way South from South Willow Street to South Webster Street and along South Othello Street from 38th Avenue South to 43rd Avenue South.
